title: Carnivores Dinosaur Hunter HD [PSN] - FULL GAME
description:
Game Overview

In the near future advances in engineering made interstellar travel possible, bringing forth the era of space exploration. Along many planets the mankind has discovered was a world very similar to Earth circa Jurassic period. The planet had a lot of islands populated with huge and wild animals, which supposedly looked just like Earth's long extinct dinosaurs. Soon enough exploration of the planet began. "DinoHunt, Inc" was established, and the company started to provide hunting trips for everyone wealthy and bold enough to take on mighty creatures inhabiting the planet.

You are one of those hunters. The game brings you to an ancient environment and lets you hunt for the most dangerous and the strongest creatures in the universe. Get a hunting license, pack up your gear, choose an island to hunt and embark on the adventure of a lifetime!
Beautiful surroundings

Visit huge realistic islands each representing a certain type of environment. There are beaches, jungles, forests, rocky plains and deserts.
Different dinosaur types

Start with an easy prey and move up the food chain eventually hunting the biggest and the deadliest creatures alive!

Get ready for the hunt

Choose between a high caliber rifle and a silent crossbow and donÃ¢â‚¬â„¢t forget your trusty side gun. And make sure to mask yourself from animals with CoverScent!
Jurassic national park

Explore the islands and observe the wildlife. You can still capture dinosaurs without killing them; just make sure to sedate animals first with tranquilizer ammo.
